@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tlxopm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v2 * ((v1 + 0.86 * v1 + 0.36) * (v2 + 0.10 / tmp + 0.70)))
    v0 = (v0 - v0)
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.42 + v0 + 0.68) * (tmp + 0.79 / v2 + 0.19)) - tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    tmp = (v2 / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.32) - tmp))
    v2 = ((0.87 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.33)) + 0.70)
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
